Régression non-linéaire

SciViews::R

Vitesse de réaction

sp <- read("../data/speed_reaction.rds")
fm1 <- nls(speed ~ SSmicmen(conc, Vm, K), data = sp)
summary(fm1)

Formula: speed ~ SSmicmen(conc, Vm, K)

Parameters:
   Estimate Std. Error t value Pr(>|t|)    
Vm  5.00209    0.02663  187.81   <2e-16 ***
K   9.95053    0.26317   37.81   <2e-16 ***
---
Signif. codes:  0 ‘***’ 0.001 ‘**’ 0.01 ‘*’ 0.05 ‘.’ 0.1 ‘ ’ 1

Residual standard error: 0.1037 on 98 degrees of freedom

Number of iterations to convergence: 0 
Achieved convergence tolerance: 1.016e-07
sp %>.%
  chart(data = ., speed ~ conc)+
  geom_point() +
  geom_line(f_aes(predict(fm1) ~ conc))

Herbicides

algae <- read("../data/algae.xlsx") 
chart(data = algae, vol ~ log(conc+1)) +
  geom_point() 

reg <- nls(vol ~ SSlogis(log(conc+1), Asym, xmid, scal), data = algae,
    trace = TRUE)

AIC(reg, reg1)
